   require ncurses libpcap
  category utility network
 attribute console
    source http://www.ex-parrot.com/pdw/iftop/download/iftop-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info home  http://www.ex-parrot.com/pdw/iftop/
      info mail  http://lists.beasts.org/mailman/listinfo/iftop-users
      desc 'network usage report similar to the top CPU usage report
It listens to network traffic on a named interface and 
displays a table of current bandwidth usage by pairs of hosts.
Handy for answering the question why is our ADSL link so slow?.'
